{
  "stem": "24409.11",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was, on that day-- in-- first of all, when Hitler was dead, when he committed suicide, I was only in a castle, just overnight sleeping on the way from one prisoner of war camp to another one.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was near [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the prisoner of war-- then-- the-- the-- a short time after that, I was in [INAUDIBLE] when I learned that Germany had surrendered unconditionally.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was-- not one of them was healthy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] There came a a commission from Germany, a [INAUDIBLE], a royal, whatever his name was, who was very eager to establish friendship with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the [INAUDIBLE], [INAUDIBLE] was involved, the commanding general of the Army [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had been Hitler's-- that's what we heard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hitler's sergeants in World War I and had been his bouncer in the meetings, in the early meetings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was very much down [INAUDIBLE] by the generals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was involved into this case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because through his hands passed Hitler's order not to make any prisoners during this war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- he didn't say it like that, Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hitler said, we will-- we have to advance with-- without showing any [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] weakness.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, he didn't say weakness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the knowledge of our acting like [INAUDIBLE] has to precede our troops.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he didn't say exactly prisoners of war will be made.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he-- as it came down, it was that prisoners were not to be made.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- but the only general I interviewed in this position was [INAUDIBLE], with whom I got a complete confession.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You see, the idea-- it was quite a split opinion in the American public, which was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
